---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Resources | Agora" description="Download tools, posters, and guides to help build the Agora in your community.">
  
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 text-zinc-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-16">
      
      <header class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">The Toolkit</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400">
          Everything you need to signal the movement and organize your local cell. Agora spreads through physical presence and shared identity.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold border-b border-zinc-800 pb-2">01. Analog Signal (Print)</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">For the streets, community boards, and local gathering spots.</p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="p-4 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex justify-between items-center group">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold">The "Exit" Poster Series</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 underline">PDF / B&W / A4 & US Letter</p>
              </div>
              <button class="bg-white text-black text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100">Download</button>
            </li>
            <li class="p-4 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex justify-between items-center group">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold">Cell Invitation Cards</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 underline">PDF / Business Card Size</p>
              </div>
              <button class="bg-white text-black text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100">Download</button>
            </li>
            <li class="p-4 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex justify-between items-center group">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold">Agora Logo Stencil</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 underline">SVG / DXF for Laser Cutting</p>
              </div>
              <button class="bg-white text-black text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100">Download</button>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold border-b border-zinc-800 pb-2">02. Digital Identity</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">For the Social Network app and internal coordination.</p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="p-4 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex justify-between items-center group">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold">Agora Brand Kit</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 underline">Logos / Typography / Colors</p>
              </div>
              <button class="bg-white text-black text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100">Download</button>
            </li>
            <li class="p-4 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex justify-between items-center group">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold">Leader Dashboard Icons</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 underline">PNG / SVG Set</p>
              </div>
              <button class="bg-white text-black text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100">Download</button>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 space-y-8">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">03. The Discourse</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-400">
            How we speak about the movement matters. These guides help Chapter Leaders navigate the transition from “online users” to “offline stewards.”
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <a href="#" class="block p-6 bg-zinc-950 rounded-2xl hover:border-white/20 border border-transparent transition">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 uppercase text-xs tracking-widest text-zinc-500">Guide</h3>
            <p class="text-white">Talking to the Loneliness Epidemic</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block p-6 bg-zinc-950 rounded-2xl hover:border-white/20 border border-transparent transition">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 uppercase text-xs tracking-widest text-zinc-500">Primer</h3>
            <p class="text-white">Understanding Neoliberal Atomization</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block p-6 bg-zinc-950 rounded-2xl hover:border-white/20 border border-transparent transition">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 uppercase text-xs tracking-widest text-zinc-500">Manual</h3>
            <p class="text-white">Stewardship vs. Subscription</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>